description: This operation will list all parts in a requested multipart upload for a sequence store.

parameters.name: sequenceStoreId
parameters.description: The Sequence Store ID used for the multipart uploads.

parameters.name: uploadId
parameters.description: The ID for the initiated multipart upload.

parameters.name: partSource
parameters.description: The source file for the upload part.

parameters.name: filter
parameters.description: Attributes used to filter for a specific subset of read set part uploads. createdAfter (datetime) --- Filters for read set uploads after a specified time. createdBefore (datetime) --- Filters for read set part uploads before a specified time.

nested_params.name: createdAfter
nested_params.description: Filters for read set uploads after a specified time.

nested_params.name: createdBefore
nested_params.description: Filters for read set part uploads before a specified time.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: Next token returned in the response of a previous ListReadSetUploadParts call. Used to get the next page of results.

nested_items.name: partNumber
nested_items.description: The number identifying the part in an upload.

nested_items.name: partSize
nested_items.description: The size of the the part in an upload.

nested_items.name: partSource
nested_items.description: The origin of the part being direct uploaded.

nested_items.name: checksum
nested_items.description: A unique identifier used to confirm that parts are being added to the correct upload.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time stamp for when a direct upload was created.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedTime
nested_items.description: The time stamp for the most recent update to an uploaded part.
